{"tid":1049488,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比利時最高學府研究組分析了超過7000場，C朗在應對壓力方面做得更加出色","createTime":"2019-03-06T09:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T11:17:36.000Z","uid":173952,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bd20ed5daf34e0e2a8b2de462958fd8198d061b9","tid":1049488,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"近日在美國波士頓召開的麻省理工學院斯隆體育分析學術會議上，比利時魯汶大學研究小組公佈了他們的最新研究成果&mdash;&mdash;研究小組認為，葡萄牙巨星C羅在應對壓力方面做得更加出色。<br />\n<br />\n研究小組總共分析了超過7000場的足球比賽，從而研究球員們在高壓下的發揮情況。項目主要負責人之一的Davis說到：&ldquo;我們嘗試建立了一種模型，用來模擬球員在拿球時承受了多少的壓力，並進一步分析該名球員在有壓力時的行為是否合理。比方說比賽進行到了第89分鐘，某名球員在拿球後需要作出是傳球還是射門的選擇，而我們的模型會分析球員的選擇是否合理，他是否良好的執行了自己的選擇，以及該選擇最後對比賽結果的影響如何。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n由於主場和客場、該支球隊當時處於情況、該比賽對球隊該賽季最終成績的影響等因素的不同，該模型顯然也會相應地去採用不同的參數。<br />\n<br />\n研究員Jan Van Haaren解釋道:&ldquo;對於一名球員來說，最理想的情況就是能夠完全不受壓力的影響、奉獻出穩定的精彩表現。我們的研究結果顯示，C羅就幾乎不受壓力影響，他的表現一直都很穩。另一方面，蘇亞雷斯和內馬爾就有點不穩定了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n編輯註：魯汶大學（荷語：KU Leuven；英語：University of Leuven）是比利時久負盛名的最高學府，世界50強高校，歐洲歷史最悠久且最受人尊敬的大學之一，也是享譽全球的世界級頂尖研究型大學。"},{"pid":"fac2d30effac22221342e63cee47908e3eda4e08","tid":1049488,"uid":13343,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亞球王小花呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144d8c48713cedd22eade817a3facbe101efd6c3","tid":1049488,"uid":174530,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:00:31.000Z","msg":"呢個post過唔到2頁"},{"pid":"4a6af7f955c2698c7c2d15014c32e49682b10671","tid":1049488,"uid":158529,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"阿朗抗壓不嬲勁 佢自己都講過 噓聲越大 佢就會當成一種鼓勵 <br />\n<br />\n而且小花四連金球 個個以為阿朗一沉不起 點知又俾佢追到金球獎平手<br />\n<br />\n鬥心抗壓呢方面真係冇得唔服佢"},{"pid":"e6e30e84c4bc27fe7be9726854db3548a666f722","tid":1049488,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"等今晚贏埋再上神台"},{"pid":"ebb35d6e0024f25bef78587d5b2c26e97927c93b","tid":1049488,"uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e6e30e84c4bc27fe7be9726854db3548a666f722","tid":1049488,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"等今晚贏埋再上神台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T12:50:08.000Z","msg":"今晚贏乜"},{"pid":"1b00cc34f89edb337233a3234bc737eb3d7c24d0","tid":1049488,"uid":83933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"由一開始踢曼比人屌獨食，之後06得罪埋朗尼比自己球迷噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去皇頭兩年又比小花壓住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩風浪未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013ab58aae1a8b9504a61ec53612640e55a106a2","tid":1049488,"uid":23385,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"上年90幾分鐘對祖球12碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大大力抽死角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1